    {
      "id": "newworker-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 785,
      "y": 430,
      "width": 390,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "LIVING WORKER (Python/FastAPI/DO)\nRoda 3x/dia (07h, 13h, 19h BRT)\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nnews_fetcher.py   Tavily -> noticias\npolling_fetcher   Pesquisas reais (1x/dia)\nimpact_analyzer   Claude Haiku -> impacto\ndelta_computer    Deterministico (sem IA)\ncalibrator        Correcao c/ pesquisas reais\ndb_updater        Aplica deltas batch\nsafety            Drift limits + snapshots\n\nMAX: +-0.03/noticia, +-0.05/dia, +-0.15/total",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#ffd43b",
