    {
      "id": "flow1-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 35,
      "y": 680,
      "width": 1140,
      "height": 180,
      "text": "EXEMPLO: \"Lula anuncia Auxilio Gas de R$120\"\n\n1. Tavily busca noticia              2. Claude Haiku analisa                    3. Delta Computer (SEM IA)\n   headline + conteudo                  Tipo: policy                              Persona P1, q_bolsa_familia=Sim:\n                                        Magnitude: 0.4                            delta = 0.4 x 0.8 x 0.03 x 2.0\n                                        Segmentos:                                = +0.019 em sentiment_lula\n                                          P1-P3: sens=0.8, positivo\n                                          M3-M5: sens=0.5, positivo              Persona C1, sem match:\n                                          C1-C3: sens=0.3, NEGATIVO              delta = 0.4 x 0.3 x 0.03 x 0.5 x (-1)\n                                        Campos: q_bolsa_familia_bom               = -0.002 em sentiment_lula\n                                               q_auxilio_emergencial\n                                                                                  4. UPDATE persona_sentiments\n                                                                                  5. Recomputa polling: Lula 46.1% -> 46.3%",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#ff6b6b",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 28,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 28,
      "isDeleted": false,
